{"tid":1860798,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎》驚！中國首席生化武器專家到達武漢","createTime":"2020-02-04T00:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T01:07:08.000Z","uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a5b48d8354c63053bb156ea73663c88230b3803","tid":1860798,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢肺炎》驚！<br />\n中國坐鎮武漢的是首席生化武器專家</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/04/phptP0ZgE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F04%2FphptP0ZgE.jpg&h=f50d8b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國湖北省武漢市「2019新型冠狀病毒」（2019-nCoV）肺炎疫情不斷蔓延，中國派出首席生化武器防禦專家陳薇少將到武漢坐鎮，她也表明「要做最壞打算」，引發中國微博網友群情譁然，急呼：「我們遭到生化攻擊了嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，中國1月26日派出具有解放軍少將軍階的中國工程院院士、軍事科學院軍事醫學研究院研究員陳薇坐鎮武漢，她也具有首席生化武器防禦專家稱號，曾於2003年SARS期間「做出醫療貢獻」，完成涉及1.4萬名醫護人員的臨床研究，證實特定藥物能保護第一線醫護人員不被感染。<br />\n<br />\n陳薇在2015年率領研究團隊研發出伊波拉病毒疫苗，使中國自主研製的伊波拉疫苗首次獲得境外臨床試驗許可，對於炭疽病毒、鼠疫也多有研究，此次前往武漢加入防疫戰線，陳薇不樂觀地表示「要做最壞打算」，她認為，若有病毒發生變異，能夠利用大數據找出原因，加快改良疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友發現首席生化武器防禦專家也在「抗疫」陣容，紛紛留言指出「為什麼生化專家開始進駐武漢？難道真的是shenghua weapon洩露了？」、「這種消息還是少轉載為妙」、「眾多事實都指向了生化戰，輿論戰」、「這種級別的人物不給絕密保護？」、「太可怕了」。<br />\n<br />\n▼許多網友在PTT上熱烈討論這個事件（圖／取自PTT）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-fnc.ebc.net.tw/EbcFnc/news/images/113959/2020/02/03/1580747404_22706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-fnc.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcFnc%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F113959%2F2020%2F02%2F03%2F1580747404_22706.jpg&h=c13b1561&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73e393f923ffb85a3bff6721b9e70a9569d058d5","tid":1860798,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T00:48:24.000Z","msg":"支那微博留言：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4467524525769040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4467524525769040&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=ec9c58eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/status/4467524525769040</a>"},{"pid":"5ef52dc087af5d4f55bde289956d086805e25429","tid":1860798,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T00:50:01.000Z","msg":"大爆炸咪算"},{"pid":"dc68fb3ca791588b1010977c74750e06d781869d","tid":1860798,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T00:53:01.000Z","msg":"為中國人帶來武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/aaf0dc1f1f6d7ba91791c944871ecc8684423e6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farchive%2Faaf0dc1f1f6d7ba91791c944871ecc8684423e6e.jpg&h=20d20a9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62e3d71c1eded67fd99f2a42a120db0a38c4e8c8","tid":1860798,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YVg5NXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVg5NXY.jpg&h=73eb36e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmyjSpE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmyjSpE.jpg&h=ef23b644&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n順便send啲大陸論壇爆料"}]}